     <period-end iso-date="2020-12-31"></period-end>
     <target>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Develop at least 1 (one) guidance note on gender analysis across all sectors of the NDCs, to better identify, understand, and describe relevance of gender differences for climate policies.
- Conduct analysis of the industry and construction sectors as priority sectors for NDCs to assess the impact of climate change on the sector and identify the specific actions for mitigation.
- Conduct analysis of the transport and infrastructure sectors as priority sectors for NDCs to assess the impact of climate change on the sector and identify the specific actions for mitigation and/or adaptation.</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
