- Analysis of the industry and construction sectors as priority sectors for NDCs to assess the impact of climate change on the sector and identify the specific actions for mitigation - conducted/published.
- Analysis of the transport and infrastructure sectors as priority sectors for NDCs to assess the impact of climate change on the sector and identify the specific actions for mitigation and/or adaptation - conducted/published
https://www.tj.undp.org/content/tajikistan/en/home/library/ghg-forecasting-in-key-sectors-and-impact-assessment-of-climate-0.html</narrative>
      </comment>
     </actual>
    </period>
    <period>
     <period-start iso-date="2021-01-01"></period-start>
     <period-end iso-date="2021-12-31"></period-end>
     <target>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Conduct stakeholder consultations on NDC revision, with government and non-government stakeholders, focusing on industry and transport sectors, as well as on gender mainstreaming.
- The 5-year or 10-year plan (timelines to be agreed with governmental stakeholders) for NDCs implementation with prioritization of specific actions to be undertaken in the near and long-term.
- Three (3) position papers for UNDP-led policy work in support of the climate action in Tajikistan, a) clearly defining UNDP&#x2019;s offer and value addition, as well as b) theories of change for proposed areas of support.</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">- The stakeholder consultation process was conducted to obtain information regarding sectoral circumstances, sectoral GHG emissions and vulnerability to climate change, as well as the existing industry and construction policy frameworks. To collect information, letters were prepared and sent on behalf of the Committee on Environmental Protection under the Government of the Republic of Tajikistan to the following relevant authorities:
- Ministry of Industry and New Technologies
- The Statistics Agency under the President of the Republic of Tajikistan
- The Committee on Construction and Architecture
- The Institute of Construction and Architecture
- The NDC Implementation Plan developed (5-10 year) and submitted to the Government and shared among NDC partnership stakeholders.
- Three (3) position papers for UNDP-led policy work in support of the climate action in Tajikistan developed.</narrative>
      </comment>
     </actual>
